%% Smart Campus Assistant — Sequence Diagram (Main Flow)
%% Render at: https://mermaid.live

sequenceDiagram
    actor S as Student
    participant F as React Frontend
    participant B as FastAPI Backend
    participant C as Question Classifier
    participant V as pgvector Store
    participant DB as Supabase DB
    participant AI as AI Service (LLM)

    S->>F: 1. Types question in chat UI
    F->>B: 2. POST /ask { question }
    
    Note over B: 3. Validate & sanitize input<br/>(length, encoding, injection guard)
    
    B->>C: 4. Classify question
    C-->>B: 5. category: schedule | general_info | technical_issue

    par RAG + Structured Data (parallel)
        B->>V: 6. Embed question → vector search<br/>(with metadata category filter)
        V-->>B: Top-5 relevant chunks
    and
        B->>DB: 7. Query structured tables by category
        DB-->>B: Matching campus_data records
    end

    B->>AI: 8. System prompt (versioned) + context + question
    AI-->>B: 9. Answer + confidence score (0.0-1.0)

    alt confidence >= 0.7
        B->>F: 10a. { answer, category, sources, confidence, prompt_version }
        F->>S: Display answer with category tag and sources
    else confidence < 0.7
        B->>F: 10b. { fallback_message, staff_contact }
        F->>S: Display fallback with contact info
    end

    B->>DB: 12. Log interaction (question, answer, category,<br/>confidence, response_time_ms, prompt_version)
